title: Ultimate Spinach - Ultimate Spinach (1967)
description:
Ultimate Spinach - Ultimate Spinach (1967).

9 songs - 49.9mb @ 192kbps CBR.

Stunning debut album from the Boston band. This classic of 1968 psychedelia includes the songs &quot;Ego Trip&quot; and the rightfully legendary &quot;(Ballad of The) Hip Death Goddess&quot;. Wonderous summery, tripped out shimmering psych melting into wah-wah fuzz guitars, vocal harmonies and druggy lyrics...

enjoy and seed :]
